## Additional Terms for Assessment Use

This assessment package is provided for use in hiring and recruitment processes.

### You MAY:
✅ Use this assessment to evaluate job candidates
✅ Modify and customize the assessment for your needs
✅ Distribute the candidate materials to job applicants
✅ Adapt the scoring rubric to your standards
✅ Share with other hiring managers in your organization

### You MAY NOT:
❌ Use candidate submissions for commercial purposes
❌ Sell or redistribute this assessment package commercially
❌ Claim authorship of the original assessment design
❌ Use candidate code in production without their explicit consent

### Best Practices:
- Treat all candidate submissions confidentially
- Delete candidate code after evaluation period
- Provide feedback when possible
- Respect candidate intellectual property
- Follow fair hiring practices

### Disclaimer:
This assessment package is provided as-is for hiring purposes. The authors
are not responsible for hiring decisions made using this assessment. Always
comply with local employment laws and regulations.
